---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="container-wide pb-14 pt-10 md:pb-16 md:pt-14">
  <div class="glow-divider mb-10"></div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Colophon</p>
      <h2 class="section-title mt-4">
        慢慢写，持续更新。
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-md text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed text-[var(--muted)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); font-style: italic;">
        这里收集教程、学习记录和一些正在发酵的灵感，让每次更新都更耐读一点。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-[0.78rem] md:items-end md:text-right">
      <p class="font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[var(--text-strong)]">
        &copy; {year} &middot; 梦付千秋
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--muted)]">
        Built with
        <a
          href="https://astro.build"
          class="text-[var(--accent)] underline decoration-[var(--accent)] underline-offset-4 hover:text-[var(--accent-deep)]"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          Astro
        </a>
        &middot;
        <span class="font-mono">v1.0</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
